            </h1>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-400 font-light leading-relaxed max-w-lg">
                16 Years of Quantitative Engineering & Algorithmic Design. <br>
                <span class="text-white font-medium">94% Verified Win Rate</span> (Last 6 Months).
            </p>
            <div class="pt-4">
                <a href="#connect" class="btn-gold px-10 py-5 rounded-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-sm inline-block text-center w-full md:w-auto">
                    Request 48-Hour Strategic Access — $90
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Pricing / Tiers -->
    <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 pb-32">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10">
            <!-- Institutional Licensing -->
            <div class="card-glass p-12 flex flex-col h-full group">
                <div class="mb-8">
                    <h3 class="text-3xl serif mb-1">Institutional Licensing</h3>
                    <span class="jp-text">機関ライセンス</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-[10px] gold-text uppercase tracking-[0.4em] mb-10 border-b border-gold/10 pb-4">Professional Access</p>
                <ul class="space-y-6 flex-grow text-gray-400 font-light text-sm">
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-4"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-gold rounded-full"></span> Upfront Licensing Fee</li>
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-4"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-gold rounded-full"></span> 20-30% Quarterly Performance Fee</li>
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-4"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-gold rounded-full"></span> Dedicated Analytics Support</li>
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-4"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-gold rounded-full"></span> Real-time Signal API Integration</li>
                </ul>
                <button class="mt-12 border border-gold/40 text-gold py-4 uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-[10px] hover:bg-gold hover:text-black transition-all duration-500">Inquire Details</button>
            </div>

            <!-- Full IP Transfer -->
            <div class="card-glass p-12 flex flex-col h-full relative overflow-hidden group">
                <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 gold-gradient px-6 py-2 text-[9px] text-black font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">Full Ownership</div>
                <div class="mb-8">
                    <h3 class="text-3xl serif mb-1">Full IP Transfer</h3>
                    <span class="jp-text">完全な知的財産の譲渡</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-[10px] gold-text uppercase tracking-[0.4em] mb-10 border-b border-gold/10 pb-4">Asset Acquisition</p>
                <ul class="space-y-6 flex-grow text-gray-400 font-light text-sm mb-10">
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-4"><span class="w-2 h-[1px] bg-gold"></span> 100% Intellectual Property Ownership</li>
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-4"><span class="w-2 h-[1px] bg-gold"></span> Tier-1 Fund Deployment Rights</li>
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-4"><span class="w-2 h-[1px] bg-gold"></span> Full Source Code & Algorithm Transfer</li>
                </ul>
                
                <div class="bg-white/5 p-6 mb-10 border-l-2 border-gold">
                    <p class="text-[11px] text-gold/80 font-medium tracking-wider leading-relaxed italic">
                        "Strictly for Institutional Entities & High-Net-Worth Individuals. Comprehensive valuation provided upon vetting."
                    </p>
                </div>

                <button class="btn-gold py-5 uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-[10px]">Initiate Acquisition Protocol</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Connect Footer -->
    <footer id="connect" class="bg-[#050505] py-32 px-8 border-t border-white/5 relative">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto text-center">
            <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl serif mb-8">Secure Direct Access.</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-light mb-20 max-w-2xl mx-auto uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-xs leading-loose">
                Click or scan below to authenticate your profile and secure a 48-Hour Strategic Access window.
            </p>

            <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-12 md:gap-24">
                <!-- LINE -->
                <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-6 group">
                    <a href="https://line.me/ti/p/YOUR_LINK" target="_blank" class="qr-frame group-hover:scale-105 group-hover:shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(212,175,55,0.25)]">
                        <img src="https://api.qrserver.com/v1/create-qr-code/?size=150x150&data=https://line.me/ti/p/YOUR_LINK" alt="LINE QR" class="qr-img">
