                        <img src="https://api.qrserver.com/v1/create-qr-code/?size=150x150&data=https://t.me/ForexFearClinicSupport" alt="Telegram QR" class="qr-img">
                    </a>
                    <span class="text-[10px] tracking-[0.4em] uppercase text-gray-600 group-hover:text-gold transition-colors">TELEGRAM</span>
                </div>

                <!-- WHATSAPP -->
                <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-6 group">
                    <a href="https://wa.me/306970265720" target="_blank" class="qr-frame group-hover:scale-105 group-hover:shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(212,175,55,0.25)]">
                        <img src="https://api.qrserver.com/v1/create-qr-code/?size=150x150&data=https://wa.me/306970265720" alt="WhatsApp QR" class="qr-img">
                    </a>
                    <span class="text-[10px] tracking-[0.4em] uppercase text-gray-600 group-hover:text-gold transition-colors">WHATSAPP</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto mt-32 text-[8px] text-gray-700 uppercase tracking-[0.4em] leading-relaxed opacity-60">
                Risk Warning: Trading foreign exchange on margin carries high risk. Past performance is not indicative of future results.
                <span class="block mt-2">投資にはリスクが伴います。過去の成果は将来の結果を保証するものではありません。</span>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-white/5 text-[10px] text-gray-800 uppercase tracking-widest">
                <p>© 2026 Forex Fear Clinic Elite. Strictly Private & Confidential.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
